    com.paydiant.android.config

  • Classes in com.paydiant.android.config used by com.paydiant.android.config 
    Class and Description
    HostContext
    The Host Context class which will hold information of the mobile gateway host which the Android SDK will communicate with.
    PaydiantApplicationConfig
    Configures and initializes the SDK to perform operations with the Paydiant mobile gateway.
